Atomic Radial Moments:
---------------------
  R-2(A) = <Rho/(r*r)>(A)
  R-1(A) = <Rho/r>(A)
  R0(A)  = <Rho>(A) = N(A)
  R+1(A) = <Rho*r>(A)
  R+2(A) = <Rho*r*r>(A)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
